subject: Colleges and Universities
School Discipline (Students)
Sex Crimes
lead_paragraph: Jameis Winston, the Heisman Trophy winner who has been accused of rape by a former student, did not attend the hearing, which focused on two of his teammates who witnessed part of the sexual encounter.
